==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: end-user
<hw>end-user</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person who uses an item of
commerce for its designed purpose; -- contrasted with those who produce
or resell the item or incorporate the item into another product.</def>
<note>Purchasers of items who are not end-users include:
<contr>reseller</contr>; <contr>value-added reseller, VAR</contr>; and
<contr>producer, manufacturer</contr>.</note>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> consumer.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

